description: Retrieves information about a signal catalog.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the signal catalog to retrieve information about.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the signal catalog.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the signal catalog.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A brief description of the signal catalog.

nested_items.name: nodeCounts
nested_items.description: The total number of network nodes specified in a signal catalog.

nested_items.name: totalNodes
nested_items.description: The total number of nodes in a vehicle network.

nested_items.name: totalBranches
nested_items.description: The total number of nodes in a vehicle network that represent branches.

nested_items.name: totalSensors
nested_items.description: The total number of nodes in a vehicle network that represent sensors.

nested_items.name: totalAttributes
nested_items.description: The total number of nodes in a vehicle network that represent attributes.

nested_items.name: totalActuators
nested_items.description: The total number of nodes in a vehicle network that represent actuators.

nested_items.name: totalStructs
nested_items.description: The total structure for the node.

nested_items.name: totalProperties
nested_items.description: The total properties for the node.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the signal catalog was created in seconds since epoch (January 1, 1970 at midnight UTC time).

nested_items.name: lastModificationTime
nested_items.description: The last time the signal catalog was modified.
